flowchart TD
  A[insight/debate/radar commands] --> B[.sdd/state/discovery-index.yaml]
  B --> C[.sdd/discovery/1-insights]
  B --> D[.sdd/discovery/2-debates]
  B --> E[.sdd/discovery/3-radar]
  B --> F[.sdd/discovery/4-discarded]

  G[breakdown/start commands] --> H[.sdd/state/backlog.yaml]
  H --> I[openspec/changes/<change-name>]
  I --> J[openspec/changes/archive]
  J --> K[.sdd/state/finalize-queue.yaml]
  K --> L[finalize command]
  L --> M[.sdd/core + .sdd/pendencias]

  N[fgap add/done] --> O[.sdd/state/frontend-gaps.yaml]
  N --> P[.sdd/state/frontend-map.yaml]
  O --> M
  P --> M

  Q[skills suggest/sync] --> R[.sdd/state/skill-catalog.yaml]
  R --> S[.<tool>/skills]